data.description: ******PRICE REDUCED**** Motivated seller! This beautiful home has been meticulously maintained and move in ready. Walking distance to Publix, Walgreens and Advent Health. Walk through the front door and see your formal living room to the left. The 25x15 great room is great for entertaining. The kitchen offers granite counters and an Island sink and all appliances. The upstairs boasts a HUGE primary bedroom with plenty of space. The bathroom is large with separate water closet. All 3 other bedrooms are good sized. Enjoy the outdoor area with a retention pond behind the house that never fills. Perfect play area for your dog or family!  This is also a VA assumable mortgage! The location of this house is perfect for a Disney fan, being within a half hour of both Disney and Legoland.  Close to shopping and all of Central Florida has to offer.
